{"tid":1759312,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"灣仔呢間蝦麵店 真係好過分","createTime":"2019-11-27T14:36:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-27T20:46:53.000Z","uid":22631,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"c9bafec77adf7100fa4e3a3f711b7c044a8d7e45","tid":1759312,"uid":22631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T14:36:18.000Z","msg":"係&lt;和你eat&gt;見到灣仔間蝦麵店有罷工同捐錢俾星火<br />\n今日就去左懲罰下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n6點幾去到只係得一枱客食緊 一坐低店員就問係咪學生<br />\n一時反應唔切 就如實答左一個係 一個唔係<br />\n<br />\n店入面雖然無寫學生免費，但老細應該落左order唔收學生錢<br />\n<br />\n到埋單個時 店員話唔洗埋單 老細話要懲罰下啲客 同店員將啲錢互推左好耐 半價又唔肯 叫佢捐左去又叫我地自己捐返 搞到最後要跑走先俾到錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />實在太過分<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講返啲野食 試左辣味蝦湯底摻摻 雖然蝦肉開左邊 搞到無乜咬口同無乜味（黃店都要改善下既），但湯底蝦味好濃郁，帶有微辣，好惹味，整體黎講都幾好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢間鋪除左灣仔，荃灣、鰂魚涌同銅鑼灣都有分店，不過就唔肯定係咪同一個老細了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n7fMid1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn7fMid1.jpg&h=d75bb4f7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f79a3abb3e32c0be41bf51c527dd3d4c60eebbbd","tid":1759312,"uid":22631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T14:37:42.000Z","msg":"手殘揀錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"290c8d566acc6a6b480f83aba124536594dba13e","tid":1759312,"uid":161681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T14:38:50.000Z","msg":"蝦麵店堅好食"},{"pid":"8a55f6404c73be98a3b95be1dda0e1e48d7efb44","tid":1759312,"uid":98784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T14:39:21.000Z","msg":"name"},{"pid":"00a1e0fdac7aa90d2084bf6a236942fc8ee60563","tid":1759312,"uid":104580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT